==English==
===Etymology===

Coined in 1972 by Stanley Cohen, who coined the phrase to describe media coverage of Mods and Rockers in Great Britain in the 1960s.

===Noun===
'''[[moral]] [[panic]]'''
#A semi-[[spontaneous]] or [[media]]-[[generated]] [[mass]] [[movement]] based on the [[perception]] that an individual, group, or community is dangerously [[deviant]] and poses a [[menace]] to society.  A public [[outcry]].

